abstract: >-
  Reproduction study for the MLRC 2026 / NeurIPS 2026 Reproducibility Track of
  Fountas et al. (ICLR 2025), "Human-inspired Episodic Memory for Infinite
  Context LLMs". Upstream code is vendored under em-llm-model/ at a pinned
  commit and is not modified.
